name: De ondergang van de Zwarte Valk

description:
The Final Hymn

An All-New Chapter in the Joshua Black saga, as "The Final Hymn begins here! The Seraph has destroyed Nevada, and the whole world is gripped in fear that another mysterious solar flare will strike again.

Meanwhile, Joshua's love life is a mess thanks to the seductive succubus Levetica. His best friend Pete has witnessed Josh use his powers, and the Grim Reaper himself is now teaching Joshua's history class! To top it all off, his little sister Jessica seems to know a whole lot but is she willing to help her big brother?

This issue also features the short story "The Purgatorist" by 102.5 The Bone's, A Cat Named Mo!
